Package oosysteme.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ManualControlCommand
    Command that gets written to bluetooth connection to change robot left and right motor speeds.
    PidChangeCommand
    Receives pid values from bluetooth connection and uses the new values for the pid strategy.
    StrategyChangeCommand
    Command is used to send new active strategy type to bluetooth connection and receive new strategy to use from bluetooth connection.
